the assets follow the following naming convention

[identifier]-[name]-[aspect-ratio]-[additional-tags].[extension]

examples:
    excelsus-logo-500x500.webp
    excelsus-logo-500x500-nobg.webp
    excelsus-logo-inverse-500x500-nobg.webp

additional tags:
note: tags are indicated by either a dash ( - ) or a period ( . )

    -nobg --> indicates that the asset does not have a background
    .old  --> indicates that the asset is no longer used and is a old variation

note: vectors do not follow this naming convention.